Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If somepony had told me when I\Nwas a blank-flank that one day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give a speech to a class\Nat Celestia's School of Magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have believed it.\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that I have\Nbeen up to the task
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because I can tell\Nthat all of you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the future\Nof Equestrian magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is in good hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. That was even better\Nthan the first eleven times!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to be able to get\Nthrough the whole speech
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking at the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight, you can't be\Nnervous about giving a speech
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to a bunch of magic students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not nervous, Spike, but\NI do have to set a good example,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,especially for\Nmagic students.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this\Nspeech has to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Let's go\Nthrough it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When Princess Celestia asked\Nme to speak to you today,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was honored to\Nhave the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to talk about my favorite\Nsubject - magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hearing impaired subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously the long-term effects\Nof the simultaneous acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of cutie marks has yet\Nto be determined, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Next slide, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can speak from\Nmy own experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that the power of cutie\Nmark magic is very real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the instance\Nof my friends and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be traced\Nto a single event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Rainbow Dash's race\Nto defend Fluttershy's honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,this Rainboom wouldn't\Nhave happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy might never have\Ndiscovered her love of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack might\Nnever have realized
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that she belonged\Non her farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And Pinkie might never have\Ndecided to leave hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be hard\Nto imagine Rarity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,without her sense\Nof fabulousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's even harder to fathom\Nwhat my life would be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Without this Rainboom,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not have gotten\Ninto magic school;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia wouldn't have\Ntaken me on as her pupil
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or sent me to Ponyville\Nto meet my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the most powerful thing\Nabout cutie mark magic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've found is the\Nconnection I share with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the real question\Nabout cutie mark magic is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,who it seems to affect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I saw her, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I looked\Nagain she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just worried what\Nshe could be up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard she wasn't very happy\Nthe last time you saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Forcing everypony in her village\Nto have the same cutie mark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't right. We\Nhad to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she's coming\Nback for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or she was just really\Ninterested in your speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Spike, I'm not\Nreally sure what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as I\Nhave my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything\Nwill be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was just\Nmore stressed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,about that speech\Nthan I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds better than\NStarlight Glimmer coming back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with an evil plot for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you say it like that,\Nit does sound kind of silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it's totally true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd tell you, but I don't\Nwant to ruin the surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't be needing that\Nanymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike. But I\Nthink we better find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we could\Nstart with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, no! Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale! Starlight\Ndoesn't even have wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looked like she\Ncould fly with just magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes open. We don't\Nknow what she has planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Rainbow Dash look\Nreally young to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't see a cutie\Nmark. You don't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We travelled back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to when Rainbow\NDash raced the bullies
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,who made fun of Fluttershy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and performed her\Nfirst Sonic Rainboom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, only Starswirl\Nthe Bearded
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,could do\Nsomething like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And even his spell\Njust went back a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Starlight do more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,than the greatest\Nwizard in Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,With this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Starswirl's spell. Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To watch the race! I don't\Nwant to miss the Rainboom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Later Rainbow Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You are about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\NStarlight's up to yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but we'd better figure it\Nout before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Twilight, I\Nthink it already is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh Twilight,\Nwhere's your castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The map pulled us back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but whatever Starlight did in\Nthe past changed things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? And how did we get\Nhere? And where's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,More like when.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Starlight altered Starswirl's\Nspell, then somehow used it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,on the map to travel into the\Npast and change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she did, the map pulled\Nus back to the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're back where...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when we started?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the map doesn't\Neven make sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire takes\Nup half of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus there's the whole\Nmissing castle thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too big to\Nhandle on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find our\Nfriends and get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a bad feeling\Nabout this, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is Ponyville.\NHow bad can things be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Sugar Cube Corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she's\Nhere, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure anything\Nwe know is the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know one place\Nthat could never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find\NPinkie or Rarity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or Fluttershy\Nor Rainbow Dash,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just knew\Nyou'd still be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.\NThis is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But who in tarnation is\NPinkie Bow and Flutter Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you for that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Honestly, the only\Nname I recognized is Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but she left for\NManehattan years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably to become a world-\Nfamous fashion designer, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not\Nthat I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Last I heard, she went\Nto help with the cause
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,like everypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The war against King Sombra\Nand the Crystal Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you\Ntwo been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's when.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is hard to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but you and I and those other\Nponies I mentioned are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bump your head on a\Ncrate of cider or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you the truth and if\Nyou come with me, I'll prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll admit, I've lived in\Nthese here parts my whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've never seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also supposed to be\Na castle that goes with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still don't see\Nwhat this has to do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with you and I\Nbeing friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Another pony named Starlight\NGlimmer used this map
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to travel through time and\Nchange things in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, the\Nmap's here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but everything\Nelse is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Different how?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for one thing,\Nwhere we came from,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no war with King Sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could tell\Nus how the war started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can figure out\Nwhen everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Crystal\NEmpire returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,it brought King\NSombra back with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it didn't take long\Nfor him to force
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,every one of his subjects to\Nfight for him against Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And even with Princess\NCelestia leading the charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It still takes every\Nlast pony in Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...doing their part...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...working day and night\Nto keep up the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe it.\NWe stopped King Sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me and all\Nof our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But we aren't friends.\NAt least not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I hope all this helped,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I really need to get\Nback to canning those apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. We're going\Nto set things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So. How are we going\Nto set things right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I DON'T KNOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing we know for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is that Starlight\Nstopped the Rainboom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that the\Nmap's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The map is connected to\Nthe Tree of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It must sense that\Nsomething isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just use Starlight's\Nversion of the spell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and go back a little earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop her before she\Neven knows we're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do now is\Nfind Starlight and st-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, finding her{\i0}\N{\i1}will be easy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But stopping her's going to\Nbe harder than you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you,\Nbut I created that spell
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to send myself back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So even when you cast it, I\Nstill get sent back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't difficult to\Nchange Starswirl's spell;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd already done the hard part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But figuring out I could use the\Nmap to go to any time or place
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and pull you along with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha! I even impressed\Nmyself with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd try to stop\Nme. You're so predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would I leave\Nthe scroll behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Touching it triggered\Nthe map to whisk you here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and watch me erase\Nthe one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that linked\Nyou with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My village was a\Nsanctuary of equality
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,where no pony's cutie mark\Nallowed them to feel superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a special place, and you\Nand your friends took it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn to take\Nsomething special from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Rainboom, you and\Nyour friends will never form
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,your special cutie mark bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutie marks for cutie marks.\NSounds like a fair trade to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now we know\Nexactly what we have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Keep your eyes peeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to stop Starlight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as Rainbow Dash\Nand those bullies race by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she could\Npop up anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Like over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember\Nhow you'd feel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,if someone said\Nthose things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just reminding\Nthese two colts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,how hurtful teasing can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. In a world where\Nevery pony is unique,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,some are bound to feel\Nmore special than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But that isn't a licence\Nto be cruel is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a shame\Nwe don't live in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,where everypony is equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would ever tease anyone\Nthere. Wouldn't that be nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it'd be nice not\Nto be teased, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's not the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can help you get\Nthrough the course this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I sure could\Nuse the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you only convinced those\Nbullies to not tease Fluttershy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop the Rainboom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not true. I convinced\Nthem not to be bullies
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,because everypony\Nshould be equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stopping the Rainboom\Nis just a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can\Nstop for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you're pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty fast? Please. I'm\Neven faster than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so, um... Hey\Nyou wanna race?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. That wouldn't\Nreally be fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're\Na full grown pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And, wait, are\Nyou an Alicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I thought\Nyou were fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I just remembered I\Nhave somewhere I need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, listen. You don't\Nhave to race me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need you to fly fast\Nenough for a Sonic Rainboom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I can't do\Nthat. Nopony can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not even a real thing.\NIt's just an old mare's tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not! I\Nknow it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you do it.\NIn the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I'm gonna go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, Twilight.\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't convince her to do the\Nimpossible? That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that\Ndidn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be\Nharder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to live in\Nthat awful future we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie? Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,SILENCE, CHANGELING!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All servants of Queen\NChrysalis found in these woods
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,must be destroyed!
